    ],
    "disclaimer": "KNOMAD bilateral data is only available for 2021 for Nepal (cells for 2022-2024 are empty in the dataset). CESLAM 2023 bilateral data uses NLSS IV survey shares applied to NRB total remittance for FY 2022/23. 2022 and 2024 estimates apply the same CESLAM/NLSS IV shares to KNOMAD total inflows for those years. All amounts in millions of US dollars (USD millions) unless noted. Nepal fiscal year runs mid-July to mid-July (e.g., FY 2022/23 = Jul 2022 - Jul 2023).",
